Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:08.83,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dollars?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.83,0:01:12.00,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't know much about them either,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:16.51,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but they have lots of crazy members. A shitload of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:18.39,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can't skip school on the first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.39,0:01:19.68,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.68,0:01:22.51,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Anyway, don't go near Heiwajima Shizuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.31,0:01:25.06,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Orihara Izaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.06,0:01:27.81,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Anyway, he's trouble, so don't get involved with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.81,0:01:29.63,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, Simon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.63,0:01:32.57,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He's supposed to get customers for that Russkie sushi shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.86,0:01:57.76,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Very good! Very good! {khorosho is russian btw}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:02:00.66,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is Russian sushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:03.70,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's yummy! It's cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:05.52,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mister, don't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:08.07,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We have Russian sushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:12.85,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.32,0:02:16.69,Drrr Hardsubs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Do you speak... Russian?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.21,0:02:21.43,Drrr Hardsubs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.14,0:02:23.26,Drrr Hardsubs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Ah, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.43,0:02:27.23,Drrr Hardsubs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Uh... Could you tell us how to get there from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.18,0:02:31.06,Drrr Hardsubs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You just have to follow that road.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:33.15,Drrr Hardsubs,,0013,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Are you tourists?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.61,0:02:34.09,Drrr Hardsubs,,0000,0006,0000,,{\blur2}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.48,0:02:36.86,Drrr Hardsubs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}This is a charming city.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:38.28,Drrr Hardsubs,,0000,0010,0000,,{\blur2}I'm sure you'll enjoy your time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.36,0:02:40.36,Drrr Hardsubs,,0000,0007,0000,,{\blur2}Thanks for the help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.12,0:02:44.24,Drrr Hardsubs,,0000,0009,0000,,{\blur2}If you feel like it, stop by for some sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.79,0:02:53.92,Drrr Hardsubs,,0000,0008,0000,,{\blur2\fscx102}Ikebukuro... This city that never sleeps stretches from east to west.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:57.46,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To the north, there's a large pleasure quarter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:03:01.83,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A sprawling city where a million people gather everyday...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:02.82,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's Ikebukuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.56,0:03:08.33,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This city is full of foreigners.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:10.33,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:12.79,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:18.45,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They came here searching for something, seeking something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:21.09,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They're here to change something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.19,0:03:31.80,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We haven't chosen class representatives yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.80,0:03:34.94,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do we have any candidates?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:37.77,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A new city.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:41.71,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No one who knows your past.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.71,0:03:44.40,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}An opportunity to become someone new.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:45.78,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}However...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.64,0:03:54.80,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sonohara...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:56.87,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sonohara Anri, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.87,0:03:58.72,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Any other candidates?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.33,0:04:01.49,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All right, you'll be the female class representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:04.59,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Take care of the rest, Sonohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.21,0:04:11.70,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:17.23,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is there a boy willing to be class representative?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:23.40,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I kinda want to do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:25.34,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but it'd be a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:28.99,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I don't want any other guy to be paired up with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:45.09,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:47.01,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Me? Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:49.22,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Man, that would be a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:50.73,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But you'll get to pair up with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:53.86,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:56.65,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:03.57,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuugamine... Mikado.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:07.53,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:08.70,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sonohara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:13.58,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U-Uh, about the meeting with the other classes tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:16.84,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I-I've never done anything like it before—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:17.80,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:19.88,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have urgent business to take care of. Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:24.92,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dude, I better not underestimate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:31.32,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To think that you used to whine when someone spread rumors in\N elementary school about you being in love with your childhood friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:35.63,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now you're a pretty active romancer, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:36.44,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:38.99,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}However, your finish was weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.99,0:05:46.28,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}With that level of engagement, your happy-go-lucky love-comedy school life will stay a dream even though you finally made it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:49.49,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I never had that intention in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:51.90,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}With that being said,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:53.24,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}let's go hit on some chicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:55.04,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Me? Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:56.15,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:06:00.00,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's my time to be popular with the ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:07.26,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I doubt they're interested in high schoolers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:11.47,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They came here seeking change.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:15.47,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But changes don't happen that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:18.98,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even if you're standing on a different stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.68,0:06:21.75,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}it's still the same old you standing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:24.73,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What? No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:26.80,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I already have a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:27.95,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:31.73,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even if a guy hits on you and invites you for a drink, it doesn't count as cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.73,0:06:33.27,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did you guys hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:36.29,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yumi's new boyfriend is in the Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:38.36,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:39.37,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isn't she scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:40.79,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, that's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:43.00,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why don't we continue this in a café?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:46.08,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aren't the Dollars like, a biker gang or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:51.80,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In this city, there are groups that commit violent acts from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:57.48,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Each group has its own color.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:07:00.28,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thus, they're called "Color Gangs."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:03.81,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But the group that exercises its influence the most
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:06.68,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}doesn't have a specific color.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.68,0:07:09.99,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Simply put, they're transparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:12.81,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's the "color" of the Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:18.66,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's said that they're a special group that recruits members through their private website.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.31,0:07:25.56,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's rumored that the recent hack-n-slash incidents are also the work of the Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:26.42,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:29.79,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Like I said, why don't you tell me the details in a café?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:32.49,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dollars?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:33.54,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.13,0:07:35.93,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What kind of people are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:37.93,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They're awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:41.31,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I heard they made a deal with the Triad recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:46.19,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, and apparently it was one of the \N\NDollars who stabbed that yakuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:49.19,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Man, this sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:53.00,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They all ran away because of that gloomy look on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:55.99,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kida-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:58.54,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:07:59.97,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:02.37,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your name was like a character's from a comic...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:04.29,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mikado-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:06.38,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're going to Toranoana. Wanna tag along?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:11.01,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Susie Yasuda-sensei's signing her works today!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:13.77,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dude, don't shout so loudly about that sort of stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.77,0:08:14.55,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:17.29,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's wrong with talking about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:17.29,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dollars?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:18.89,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, I've heard of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:22.06,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My friend told me a rumor today...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:24.58,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, I've never really seen them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:26.77,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do they even exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.86,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You think they're just a fictional group made up on the Net?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:30.69,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uh... I'm not really sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:35.41,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But if they really do exist, it's best \N\Nnot to get involved with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:36.66,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dollars?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:42.52,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They always fight against the Flame Haze that's sealed under the Sunshine 60, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:44.16,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're wrong, Yumacchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:48.42,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They're angels that fly in the sky, show their panties, and shout, "Pipiru Pirupiru."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.87,0:08:51.43,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you asking about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:53.70,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:56.88,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did the stories scare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.88,0:08:59.38,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've heard a lot of rumors too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:09:01.38,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They're very dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:03.31,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:05.89,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You shouldn't get too curious and go near them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.89,0:09:08.27,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You know the deal about curiosity and the cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:10.78,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kadota-san, you're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:14.11,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're like the mature older brother of the protagonist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:16.95,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Totally the dream man of girls into "dandy daddies."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:17.63,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.63,0:09:18.34,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:21.91,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There are places you shouldn't go to in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.34,0:09:20.36,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tsundere hero spotted!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:24.60,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your tummy won't be funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:26.92,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You should give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:29.92,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}One time won't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:32.44,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Man, I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.44,0:09:33.42,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:36.93,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Want to have something before we—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:39.54,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's the Headless Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.54,0:09:40.32,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:47.85,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come on, why all this occult stuff in broad daylight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:51.12,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Such a hard worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:56.24,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sometimes, there are people who are swallowed by the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:58.82,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And there are people who look for them desperately...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:00.83,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:02.85,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sure I can find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:05.83,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My love will summon her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.35,0:10:14.62,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Harima-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:20.22,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Harima-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:35.71,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I-I'm sorry! I thought you were someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:42.74,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And the city is full of danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:47.70,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.45,0:10:49.71,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Like here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:51.21,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, wanna have a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:56.50,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:07.33,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He was supposed to be seeking change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:11.15,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0015,,{\be1}You serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:16.11,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0015,,{\be1}He thought that something would change,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:18.97,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0015,,{\be1}that something would happen in this new city.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:20.13,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0015,,{\be1}However,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:25.16,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}a deep darkness lurking in the shadows of the seemingly glamorous city was awaiting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:28.32,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}His legs felt cramped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:33.68,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He was losing his nerves from the anxiety of his inability to live in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.68,0:11:35.75,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I understand how you feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.37,0:11:39.40,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}On the train, you get treated as a molester.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:41.11,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}On the street, you get shady invitations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:43.25,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}At home, you get in arguments with your neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:45.69,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And if that weren't enough, there's the Headless Rider and the Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.69,0:11:47.51,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's Tokyo, the concrete jungle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:48.52,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}However!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:50.06,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Get over it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:52.39,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you pledge to be a bona fide Ikebukuronian,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:55.27,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}you will overcome this ordeal, Mikado!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:58.11,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, you! Ryuugamine Mikado!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:04.39,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, I'm with you, so no worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.36,0:12:06.24,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kida-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:10.30,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, and when hitting on chicks, be sure to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.30,0:12:11.30,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:15.56,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't think hitting on MILFs is a good idea though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:16.91,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.91,0:12:19.63,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm just talking to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:28.48,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, haven't you gotten a bit cocky ever since Harima Mika disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:30.39,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I heard you became the class rep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:32.09,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aw, she's being bullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:33.87,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And the bullies are so awfully clichéd.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:37.26,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}With that much makeup, even I'm not scared of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:39.07,Drrr Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Youko's boyfriend is in the Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:40.11,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hiroshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:42.78,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yo! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:47.16,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Imma call my Dollars bros, so let's get this shit rollin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:47.66,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:51.29,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}People like this can be found anywhere in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.15,0:12:55.49,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Having so many clichés is actually refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:58.87,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uh, I better go help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.87,0:13:00.80,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But how would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:03.99,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey! Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:06.60,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No... I'll get my ass kicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:07.46,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:10.34,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wow, what a coincidence, Sonohara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:10.94,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:12.63,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Whoa, he's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.87,0:13:12.63,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:14.31,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:15.14,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bullies?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.18,0:13:18.46,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're planning to stop them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:25.44,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And in this city, unfathomable events occur frequently.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:28.03,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U-U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:29.03,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:30.53,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}H-Hey... Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:31.58,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:33.58,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}H-Hey... Wai—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.11,0:13:40.00,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:42.74,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}E-Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:45.22,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You bullies are lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:47.13,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a terrible thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:49.70,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's none of your business, old fart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:54.79,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, it's certainly none of my business if you get punched or die in a corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:14:00.47,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even if I punch you, and you call me an "old fart" despite me still being twenty three,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:03.41,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}it doesn't change the fact that we're absolutely not related.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.41,0:14:04.15,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.10,0:14:06.82,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Humans are so weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.31,0:14:11.07,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, I'm not into punching girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.09,0:14:17.39,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:22.17,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll make stomping on a girl's cell phone my hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:34.60,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's with him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:38.72,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I got bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:42.56,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm done with that hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:45.06,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hi-Hiroshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:46.81,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yo! Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.81,0:14:48.17,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:49.77,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.77,0:14:50.57,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You wanna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:52.62,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aw, I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:54.53,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Y-You fucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:57.95,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:10.73,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:15.54,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You'll pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:22.60,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kamaitachi cometh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:29.60,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But hey, it's really admirable to save a bullied girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.73,0:15:35.67,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's been a while, Kida Masaomi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:36.79,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:37.44,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.44,0:15:40.23,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's Raira Academy's uniform, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:41.87,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Grats on being admitted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:44.00,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:47.75,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's unusual to see you in Ikebukuro, Izaya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:51.25,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So this is the Orihara Izaya I shouldn't piss off?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:56.55,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, he's just a friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:16:00.00,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Orihara Izaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:01.58,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:04.18,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I-I'm Ryuugamine Mikado.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.18,0:16:06.23,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sounds like an A/C unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:10.44,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What brings you to Ikebukuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.44,0:16:12.82,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I just came here to see someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:15.15,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I'm done with that already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:22.64,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:24.84,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Was that the trash can from the convenience store?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:26.39,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It literally flew...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.39,0:16:27.00,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:28.80,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:34.51,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Izaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.92,0:16:39.93,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A bartender?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:43.77,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Didn't I tell you never to come back to Ikebukuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.65,0:16:48.52,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't hear you, Izaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:50.57,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shizu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:54.31,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Weren't you working at the West Gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:56.11,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I got fired a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:17:00.09,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And didn't I tell you to stop calling me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.09,0:17:03.37,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My name is Heiwajima Shizuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:06.72,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Heiwajima Shizuo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.72,0:17:08.50,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Another one of the people I shouldn't piss off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:13.16,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, come on, Shizu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.16,0:17:16.72,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're still pissed because I pinned that crime on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:18.77,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm not pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:20.93,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I just want to beat the crap out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:27.78,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jeez, when you get violent, no logic or reason reaches you, Shizu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:29.95,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh boy, what should I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:33.73,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let me off the hook already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:43.58,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey! That's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:52.68,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You got some balls to fuck with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.68,0:17:55.47,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We'll show you what it means to make fun of the Dollars—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.28,0:17:58.20,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A bartender outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:18:00.94,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No way! He wasn't here a moment ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:03.63,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}H-Heiwajima Shizuo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.63,0:18:05.35,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:11.01,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}People lose the ability to think rationally when they're scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:27.83,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You just hit my head, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:32.05,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You know that hitting a vital spot can kill someone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.05,0:18:35.84,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You hit me there knowing that it could be fatal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.19,0:18:40.64,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That means you have no complaints about what I do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:47.47,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Those who wield a great power
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:50.10,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}will awaken instinctive fears in others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:52.84,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He's like the embodiment of the word "violence."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:55.02,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He's like someone who lives off of violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.02,0:18:59.58,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, he  {\i0}is{\i1} violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.09,0:19:13.00,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You cowards! Don't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:17.46,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:25.72,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:36.07,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:37.35,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.35,0:19:38.68,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He jumped from above?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.68,0:19:42.61,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let me answer the question in your head, even though it's not the one you should be asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:47.41,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was just making a delivery to a regular customer living at the top of that building.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:49.16,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Simon, you bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:52.54,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shizuo, it's not good to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:53.71,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:55.04,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:06.63,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}H-Hey, Mikado!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:08.39,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:11.61,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What? You serious?!
