Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:22.97,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.49,0:20:37.79,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.18,0:20:41.76,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The city also gives presents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:45.93,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A very tiny, yet great miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.65,0:20:48.97,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The adventure he has been desiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.97,0:20:51.93,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A possibility for the start of a new story.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.40,0:20:53.63,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And...
