Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.66,0:20:59.68,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.68,0:21:01.61,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please excuse me.
