Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.44,0:21:19.49,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I found...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.22,0:21:22.09,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.21,0:21:31.93,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I heard the Dollars did it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.93,0:21:33.14,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah! Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:36.44,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They fought with a guy named Heiwajima Shizuo in broad daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:37.75,Drrr Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I heard the Dollars picked a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.75,0:21:40.94,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A fight between Shizuo and the Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:42.61,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:44.19,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, that's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.19,0:21:46.17,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I happened to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.17,0:21:49.49,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They were just impostors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:51.03,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.03,0:21:56.06,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Recently, people who called themselves the \N\NDollars attacked and robbed a pedestrian.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.06,0:21:56.99,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.99,0:22:01.04,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The Dollars are so scary and merciless.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.04,0:22:03.59,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You better watch your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.59,0:22:05.09,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}'Kay. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.09,0:22:06.52,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They're really scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.52,0:22:07.97,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.40,0:22:14.25,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Izaya came to Ikebukuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.25,0:22:18.94,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just when I was going to kill him, Simon got in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:25.03,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But... why did he come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.81,0:22:29.70,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This city is full of foreigners.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:35.04,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They came here searching for something, seeking something...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.48,0:22:38.29,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They're here to change something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:40.75,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Welcome! Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.75,0:22:42.50,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:44.34,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eat some sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.85,0:24:17.10,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0015,,{\be1}Hey, listen to my story till the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.10,0:24:22.02,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0015,,{\be1}The very unique story about me and her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.56,0:24:24.48,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0015,,{\be1}Next time: Alone With Just Your Shadow For Comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.94,0:24:30.12,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0015,,{\be1}I'm sure you'll be {\i1}non compos mentis{\i0} and trembling in fear.
